{"text_id":146337,"tokens":["###"," How"," to"," Buy"," Small"," Business"," Insurance","\n\n","Running"," a"," small"," business"," entails"," numerous"," respon","sibilities",","," and"," one"," of"," the"," most"," crucial"," is"," securing"," the"," right"," insurance"," coverage","."," Small"," business"," insurance"," protects"," your"," enterprise"," from"," potential"," risks"," and"," liabilities",","," ensuring"," longevity"," and"," stability","."," Here","\u2019","s"," a"," comprehensive"," guide"," to"," help"," you"," navigate"," the"," process"," effectively",".","\n\n","####"," Research"," Your"," State","\u2019","s"," Insurance"," Requirements","\n\n","First",","," it","\u2019","s"," essential"," to"," understand"," your"," state","\u2019","s"," insurance"," mandates","."," Each"," state"," has"," specific"," requirements"," that"," can"," include"," general"," liability"," insurance",","," workers","'"," compensation"," insurance",","," and"," disability"," insurance","."," Visit"," your"," state","'","s"," department"," of"," insurance"," website"," or"," consult"," with"," a"," local"," business"," advisor"," to"," get"," the"," correct"," information",".","\n\n","####"," Carry"," Workers","\u2019"," Compensation"," Insurance"," to"," Protect"," Against"," Employee"," Injuries","\n\n","Workers","'"," compensation"," insurance"," is"," mandatory"," in"," almost"," all"," states","."," This"," insurance"," covers"," medical"," expenses"," and"," wage"," replacement"," for"," employees"," who"," get"," injured"," at"," work","."," Ensure"," you"," have"," this"," coverage"," to"," protect"," both"," your"," employees"," and"," your"," business"," from"," potential"," lawsuits",".","\n\n","####"," Pay"," for"," Unemployment"," Insurance"," Through"," Taxes","\n\n","Unemployment"," insurance"," is"," typically"," funded"," via"," state"," and"," federal"," payroll"," taxes","."," Ensure"," you","\u2019","re"," compliant"," with"," these"," tax"," paym